<!--
  OASIS XML catalog mapping PDS4 schema URLs to local copies.
  Covers all namespaces used by CSS labels (IM 1G00 and 1N00).

  All rewritePrefix values use "./" — a relative URI resolved against
  this catalog file's own location by the XML resolver (OASIS XML
  Catalogs 1.1 §7.1.2).  Pass the absolute path to this file via
    validate -C /absolute/path/to/schemas/catalog_all.xml
  and schema lookups will resolve correctly on any machine.
-->

